<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_f24f9386-32d6-4edb-b862-1b035aafd472" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/><facet building="Class 10b"/></meta><sptc>11.2.1</sptc><title id="_f1b779ee-8f5b-4f3e-af75-143088db4971">Explanation of terms</title><archive-num>2019: 3.9.1.0</archive-num><subclause id="_938ad0bd-9784-403a-a497-418448cb0c0c" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_e9fd36fd-5302-430a-8ebd-5730c58f3234">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/867_0.6.0.xml#_a1de7ac0-2073-4e13-bb4c-3b96ad4de3a4" id="_5bd1586b-9e6b-4533-93d4-63793de7fc93" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="image-reference">Figure 11.2.1</xref> depicts stairway members and associated terminology used to describe them in the ABCB Housing Provisions.</p></subclause><subclause id="_6b89e3e0-ff5a-4620-b167-a65bc220598a" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_c2106fe7-518d-4b92-9f12-fdf61e39239e">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>Some items such as barriers and handrails have been omitted for clarity.</p></subclause><image-reference conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/867_0.6.0.xml" id="_a1de7ac0-2073-4e13-bb4c-3b96ad4de3a4"><num/><title id="_bb09a76a-6a9a-4439-a2c3-427103dbdedb"/></image-reference><callout id="_22d457ce-d693-427a-8c92-652b8dd53e94"><callout-type ncc-info-type="info"/><title id="_dadc6ed4-c8d9-427c-9fb1-e8a2ee8b1efc">Alpine areas</title><p>The requirements of this Part are to be read in conjunction with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/4228_0.3.0.xml#_0bcbd46f-dd9f-4fba-80d9-b679288c0ac2" id="_84507496-3b21-44ba-b886-55e2423f3a02" scope="local" type="part">Part 12.2</xref> where a building is located in an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1183_1.9.0.xml#_a3d630dc-9b91-4e55-a890-971223fe3a75" id="_d3ff84db-6836-4b8c-82f8-713ca3a3e6bd" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">alpine area</xref> and contains an external stairway or ramp.</p></callout><callout id="_ce6234db-da0e-4a4a-a70c-d6357de6473d"><callout-type ncc-info-type="info"/><title id="_fba54663-5f23-4170-b9d0-a66e6c4cef0a">Room heights</title><p><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/4218_0.2.0.xml#_1f878cc2-b8f9-409d-923a-edc4b53f9944" id="_7851ed55-9910-4c93-8bd9-b97ec1047ba5" scope="local" type="part">Part 10.3</xref> contains the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_0d7f7ff1-2fd7-4856-aa15-96bd15408014" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> height for a ceiling above a stairway, ramp or <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1357_2.1.0.xml#_68f79d99-aa42-455d-86ad-cae355bfc435" id="_7fb5aab3-8cac-4648-ae94-cad99c42b518" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">landing</xref>, measured vertically above the nosing line of stairway treads or the floor surface of a ramp or <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1357_2.1.0.xml#_68f79d99-aa42-455d-86ad-cae355bfc435" id="_1f8128cd-677f-4b80-9841-9195ac321016" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">landing</xref>.</p></callout></clause>